OL,3,CMPs to debate social media ban for
OL,4,Cunder-16s after support for petition
OL,6,FMPs will discuss a ban on social media
OL,7,Ffor children under the age of 16 on
OL,8,FMonday afternoon after more than
OL,9,F128,000 people signed a petition
OL,10,Fcalling for the ban.
OL,12,FThe petition says social media
OL,13,Fcompanies shouldn't let those under 16
OL,14,Fcreate social media accounts as they
OL,15,Fare "having more of a negative impact
OL,16,Fto children than a positive one."
