OL,3,CMPs to debate social media ban for
OL,4,Cunder-16s after support for petition
OL,6,FThe debate on children's use of social
OL,7,Fmedia and smartphones has gained
OL,8,Fmomentum in recent years.
OL,10,FThe campaign group "Smartphone Free
OL,11,FChildhood", created last year, now has
OL,12,Fa community of more than 150,000
OL,13,Fparents working together to change the
OL,14,Fculture around kids and smartphones.
OL,16,FThe group says "the issue has become
OL,17,Fone of the defining parenting
OL,18,Fchallenges of our time."
