OL,3,CMPs to debate social media ban for
OL,4,Cunder-16s after support for petition
OL,6,FThe debate in Westminster Hall will be
OL,7,Fled by Labour MP Tony Vaughan, who is
OL,8,Fa member of the Petitions Committee,
OL,9,Fand MPs from all parties can take
OL,10,Fpart. The government will send a
OL,11,Fminister to respond.
OL,13,FIn a response to the petition last
OL,14,FDecember, the government said it was
OL,15,Fnot "currently minded to support a ban
OL,16,Ffor children under 16".
