OL,6,FThe statement went on to say:
OL,7,F"Children face a significant risk of
OL,8,Fharm online and we understand that
OL,9,Ffamilies are concerned about their
OL,10,Fchildren experiencing online bullying,
OL,11,Fencountering content that encourages
OL,12,Fviolence, or other content which may
OL,13,Fbe harmful. We will continue to do
OL,14,Fwhat is needed to keep children safe
OL,15,Fonline.
